{"tid":2229378,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美不受理共產黨員移民 胡錫進：讓中國留住人才","createTime":"2020-10-04T10:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T00:55:16.000Z","uid":337052,"like":184,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7c9be3fff92a02e8bbdb12ca67a11d7dd0800d","tid":2229378,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:51:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">【中美角力】美不受理共產黨員移民 胡錫進：讓中國留住人才</span></strong><br />\n 國情動向 17:21 2020/10/04 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2765000/2768449/1004_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2765000%2F2768449%2F1004_1024.jpg&h=ed9f3f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 美不受理共產黨員移民 胡錫進：讓中國留住人才<br />\n<br />\n針對美國公民及移民服務局2日發政策指引，明文指出凡申請移民的共產黨員，都不會獲受理，<span class=\"red\">《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進在推特指出，中國有許多傑出的人才是共產黨員。美國的決定消除了他們的幻想，這有助於在中國留住更多的人才。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國公民及移民服務局的通告指，相關政策指引據美國國會通過的議案提出，以保障美國安全；除非有豁免，任何或曾經是共產黨及其他極權政黨成員身份，只要有移民傾向的外國人，都是不允許進入美國的，移民局官員皆可依此新規拒絕核准其調整身分。例如人在美國境內的共產黨員，申請將身份調整為合法永久居民的身份時，將有可能不會通過綠卡申請。<br />\n<br />\n通告指，此新增內容，主要是開始嚴格執行聯邦移民法的要求。也就是說，相關政策新規將阻止中共黨員在美國獲得綠卡或移民身份。《紐約時報》7月時曾引述知情者稱，美國政府考慮禁止中共黨員入境美國，當時許多人認為美國限制與中共黨員往來的法案或不會短期內實施。而根據中國今年公佈的數據，現存註冊的中共黨員人數為9191.4萬人。<br />\n<br />\n針對美國的新政策，胡錫進在推特指出，中國有許多傑出的人才是共產黨員。美國的決定消除了他們的幻想，這有助於在中國留住更多的人才，非黨員也會減少移民美國的興趣。<br />\n<br />\nMany outstanding talents in China are Communist Party members. The decision by the US helps keep more talents in China since it takes out their illusion. Not bad. What&rsquo;s more, non-CPC members now have much less interest in immigrating to the US.<br />\n<br />\n世界新聞網則引述移民律師周東發說，這個新政策，美移民局去年就開始默默操作，多位同行的客戶，去年於入境時遭移民官詢問是否為共產黨員，因據實回答，遭移民官拒絕入境並直接遣返。他說，這項新政策，是特朗普政府對華總方針的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2768449/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%97%E7%90%86%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E9%BB%A8%E5%93%A1%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%20%20%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%EF%BC%9A%E8%AE%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%99%E4%BD%8F%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2768449%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%258A%259B%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2585%25B1%25E7%2594%25A2%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%2520%2520%25E8%2583%25A1%25E9%258C%25AB%25E9%2580%25B2%25EF%25BC%259A%25E8%25AE%2593%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25BD%258F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%258D&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil7O6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=6e21ce4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2768449/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%97%E7%90%86%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E9%BB%A8%E5%93%A1%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%20%20%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%EF%BC%9A%E8%AE%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%95%99%E4%BD%8F%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D</a>"},{"pid":"3f73c3e63ca160465dca47910f3f5429e6bdadf6","tid":2229378,"uid":337052,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:52:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HuXijin_GT/status/1312659060030795776?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHuXijin_GT%2Fstatus%2F1312659060030795776%3Fs%3D20&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil7O6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=f36e13ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHuXijin_GT%2Fstatus%2F1312659060030795776%3Fs%3D20&h=35e91e04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HuXijin_GT/status/1312659060030795776?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"8d8f1172449640cd2fdb43de4d3ea658bbd606ca","tid":2229378,"uid":108016,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:52:33.000Z","msg":"支那手 joke: 好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wai